metadata.name: The Heavens
metadata.description:
High above the clouds in the Himalayas of Nepal, three climbers walk towards the verge before dissapearing into the clouds on their journey into the valley below. 

This was a magical moment, that simply cannot be repeated, with some truly mystical cloud conditions. The photo was take at an elevation of 6000m above sea-level in freezing conditions while climbing Mount Manaslu (8,163m) in the Himalayas of Nepal.

This is a 1/1 edition and a physical print will be offered upon request to the new owner of 'The Heavens'.
